Version 1.2 (2015-09-25)
-----------

* Improvements

- Added the option to compile Ops as a library.


Version 1.1.1 (2012-11-13)
-------------

* Bug fix

- Added Python library at linking stage so that the SWIG module can be built
  under MacOS.


Version 1.1 (2012-03-30)
-----------

* Improvements

- Added 'Ops::IsTable()'.
- Modified "SConstruct" so that the Python module may be built under MS
  Windows.

* Bug fix

- When an error occurred, the exception was sometimes instantiated but not
  thrown.


Version 1.0.1 (2011-07-11)
-------------

* Bug fix

- The stack was not cleared in 'Ops::Exists', which could lead to a crash
  after numerous calls to 'Ops::Exists'.


Version 1.0 (2010-09-05)
-----------

First tagged version.


The development started on 28 May 2010.
